Simplest possible RSS to email gate.

Set up FROMADDR, PASSWORD, SMTP_HOST, MAIL_RCPT values in config.json file (file format is, 
obviously, JSON).
And also set your feeds in the end of feeds.json file.

Note: information about posts we received is stored in base.pkl file (Pickle Python serialization).
No database support.

-- dennis(a)yurichev.com
